3j">elias.touil</p><p class="chakra-text css-ni95y">2 years ago</p><div class="chakra-stack css-16kr8nk"><p class="chakra-text css-10zovpx">PostgreSQL</p></div></div></div><div class="chakra-wrap css-19ug521"><ul class="chakra-wrap__list css-19lo6pj"><div class="Markdown_reactMarkdown__X0aZ_"><p><strong>@Andrew Shi</strong></p>
<p>This may be problematic, the BETWEEN operator is lying to you.
I read that the BETWEEN operator will be inclusive, including December 31st.</p>
<p>The problem is that the time of December 31, if not provided, will default to 00:00:00, meaning any message posted on that date is excluded from your query.</p>
<pre><div style="text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; color: rgb(144, 164, 174); background: rgb(250, 250, 250); font-family: &quot;Roboto Mono&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; overflow: auto; position: relative; margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 1.25em 1em;"><code style="white-space: pre; background: inherit;"><span>SELECT user_id, EXTRACT('days' from MAX(post_date) - MIN(post_date)) as days_between
</span>FROM posts
WHERE post_date BETWEEN DATE('01/01/2021') AND DATE('01/01/2022')
GROUP BY user_id
HAVING COUNT(1) &gt; 1</code></div></pre></div></ul></div><div class="css-lxox7m"><div class="css-1qofolz"><div class="chakra-stack css-9hjtr8"><button type="button" class="chakra-button css-19khf33"><svg viewBox="0 0 14 12" focusable="false" class="chakra-icon css-6hvw10" stroke-width="1.5"><svg width="14" height="12" viewBox="0 0 14 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M6 11L1 6M1 6L6 1M1 6H13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="strokeWidth" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></svg></button><p class="chakra-text css-35ezg3">4</p><button type="button" class="chakra-button css-1wvw69"><svg viewBox="0 0 14 12" focusable="false" class="chakra-icon css-1174pge" stroke-width="1.5"><svg width="14" height="12" viewBox="0 0 14 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M6 11L1 6M1 6L6 1M1 6H13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="strokeWidth" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></svg></button></div><button type="button" class="chakra-button css-ckyald" hidden=""><span class="chakra-button__icon css-1wh2kri"><svg viewBox="0 0 14 14" focusable="false" class="chakra-icon css-onkibi" aria-hidden="true"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M7 5V9M9 7H5M13 7C13 7.78793 12.8448 8.56815 12.5433 9.2961C12.2417 10.0241 11.7998 10.6855 11.2426 11.2426C10.6855 11.7998 10.0241 12.2417 9.2961 12.5433C8.56815 12.8448 7.78793 13 7 13C6.21207 13 5.43185 12.8448 4.7039 12.5433C3.97595 12.2417 3.31451 11.7998 2.75736 11.2426C2.20021 10.6855 1.75825 10.0241 1.45672 9.2961C1.15519 8.56815 1 7.78793 1 7C1 5.4087 1.63214 3.88258 2.75736 2.75736C3.88258 1.63214 5.4087 1 7 1C8.5913 1 10.1174 1.63214 11.2426 2.75736C12.3679 3.88258 13 5.4087 13 7Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></svg></span>0 replies</button></div></div></div><div class="css-f9apze"><div class="css-172hjuw">